Coloration in life. Mature male and female eyes aqua blue in upper half and pale violet below (
Fig. 6
). Dorsal thoracic stripes and pale abdominal markings yellow. Male with first lateral thoracic stripe pale yellow, female off white. Second lateral thoracic stripe in both male and female off white. Juvenile males with dorsal yellow spot on S 9–10 possibly becoming obscured with maturity.
